Feature: CSSPPFIP-30 User Details Cell

As a user I want to be able to see details of each player in the general results

Scenario background: 
	Given I have Internet connection
	And I run the app
	And the app has connection with the server
	And I acquired configuration file to send the game state to the server

Scenario: player's details window
	When I click on a player's line in the general results table
	Then I am able to see a window with the following player's details in the following order: 
	
	|photo or avatar with player's country flag in the upper right corner|
	|nick|
	|clan|
	|real name|
	|country|
	|steam profile button|

Scenario: player's details window
	Given I click on a player's line in the general results table
	And I put the app in the background
	When I go back to the app
	Then I should be able to see the window with details of a player I clicked on in general results






